sion in table 4.6, indicating that endogeneity is not a major concern. Table 4.8.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f98c5a24-4586-45ce-9102-2c5ad89ff3c2": {"__data__": {"id_": "f98c5a24-4586-45ce-9102-2c5ad89ff3c2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/blame-it-rain-gender-differentiated-impacts-drought-agricultural-wage-and-work-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Blame it on the Rain?: Gender differentiated impacts of drought on agricultural wage and work in India", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/blame-it-rain-gender-differentiated-impacts-drought-agricultural-wage-and-work-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "410bed1808fbab75c9a660632c317656df76ad4a8cc4130a8d753da96bc33a63"}, "2": {"node_id": "80b7df73-1c58-4c02-a454-6d4072b70915", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/blame-it-rain-gender-differentiated-impacts-drought-agricultural-wage-and-work-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "a2e77f4b71f16cc5236095a6aa56127cc36f20440a8ed3970490b6704b154108"}}, "hash": "2c4d1175991d43824a2d722fadb3950036d312c8ba05f1bcde26bfbcc3eb9592", "text": "Table 4.8. Impact of rainfall shocks on wages: Two-stage least squares estimates Female wage Male wage Wage ratio RainShock 0.153*** 0.102** 0.051 (0.048) (0.048) (0.045) RainShock*Rice -0.008 -0.069** 0.061** (0.033) (0.