 the provision of and employment under public works; (d) gratuitous assistance to the elderly and persons with disabilities; (e) establishment of cattle camps; (f) supplying fodder to maintain healthy livestock;(g) granting loan waivers; (h) offering concessions for water, electricity fees and supply of chlorine to disinfect drinking water on the likelihood that water from shallow levels is likely to be contaminated; and (i) establishing medical camps for health check-ups and immunization.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "04f005c8-6b7c-4ca5-909e-ddabffdb7bed": {"__data__": {"id_": "04f005c8-6b7c-4ca5-909e-ddabffdb7bed", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/blame-it-rain-gender-differentiated-impacts-drought-agricultural-wage-and-work-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Blame it on the Rain?: Gender differentiated impacts of drought on agricultural wage and work in India", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/blame-it-rain-gender-differentiated-impacts-drought-agricultural-wage-and-work-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "9573d0bfc5264dab0172513169fbfe380a20f830d9e2dd6cc2af55af7ff0d003"}, "2": {"node_id": "47eb0c91-cfba-444b-b8c5-176d2fb748e0", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/blame-it-rain-gender-differentiated-impacts-drought-agricultural-wage-and-work-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Pr