tional decision makers and law makers, need to know about the importance of the Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Discrimination Against Women (CEDAW). It is designed as a simple, user-friendly guide to familiarise legislators with CEDAW. It does not seek to go into detail on the technicalities of the Convention, as there are already a number of global and regional resources which do that already. The most relevant of these have been listed in Annex 1 of the Pocket Guide for easy reference. This Guide draws on existing Pacific and international resources on CEDAW produced by UNIFEM, the Regional Rights and Resources Team (RRRT), the Inter-Parliamentary Union (IPU) and the Fiji Women\u2019s Rights Movement (FWRM). The Pocket Guide complements the existing RRRT CEDAW pamphlet, \u201cAll About", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8ec6aa5b-92ec-4bc7-92b6-b7f55a975b49": {"__data__": {"id_": "8ec6aa5b-92ec-4bc7-92b6-b7f55a975b49", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/cedaw-pocket-guide-pacific-parliamentarians", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "CEDAW: A Pocket Guide for Pacific Parliamentarians", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/cedaw-pocket-guide-pacific-parliamentarians", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "249558a0d64efdd41d4eb46dd3ec3d434678b5d090269475f037ff3c567e0a6a"}, "3": {"node_id": "6dbbed7c-3390-4156-9e7b-0532374ac558", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publicat